as real-world data does. So I built Pandera in Python to lower that barrier to entry,

00:06:10.440 --> 00:06:16.920
to create your schema, and then iterate on it over time and collaborate on a code-first

00:06:16.920 --> 00:06:22.279
artifact that will validate your data. And my hope here is that organizations that use

