00:14:06.900 --> 00:14:12.260
Pandera also provides some additional nice things to refine your schema and refine the

00:14:12.260 --> 00:14:17.859
validation routine you want to apply to your data. And the way you do this is you define

00:14:17.859 --> 00:14:25.580
a config class underneath your schema. And if you say coerce equals true, Pandera, when

00:14:25.580 --> 00:14:30.739
